<br>
Shintou feels that since every character in the game that is to be here for a while is likely to affect those around him....some more than others...it effects our world. By PLing others...it may not take away form their ability to work well in a group...but it takes away from the RP'ness of the character. I agree with this for one should have to fight to get up to those high levels....every character should be considered different than those on other servers on this server from a RP'ers standpoint. PLing is not RP'ing when done by a level 50 for a level 1....trying to RP it is VERY FAR FETCHED with ANY explanation one could come up with. I can say ive never read a fantasy novel of any type where a king sat behind a 'noskill' and said...&quot;Let him kill it&quot;...while he sat and healed the &quot;noskill&quot;. The King would simply kill the beast and continue. This i agree with. This i think is Shintou's point.(correct me if im wrong)<br>
<br>
<br>
Now...FaF...their point. This friend of theirs from another server has came and made a character on our fine server. They have enjoyed eachother's play and wish to play together. The problem is, she is 1st level and they are 50th. so the only way to get her up to their level fast is to PL...otherwise it will be weeks if not months til they can group together again. I do sympathize to this.<br>
<br>
Now, i would not bar any from playing on this server because they dont RP. But i would like to see as much RP on this server as possible and would so encourage it. Im sorry FaF, but i feel PL is not RP. By doing this PL, those involved i feel their characters are NOT true RP'ers for my example above i feel proves.<br>
<br>
I would not kick them out....but i would show my displeasure if after reading my post they continued. For as i see it, they are not going along with what the spirit of this server was meant to be.<br>
<br>
Dhugal Forgefyre<br>
